headline: EOG Resources (EOG) Q4 2025 Earnings Transcript
summary: 2025 was a remarkable year for EOG Resources, Inc. Overall, our year was characterized by disciplined capital allocation, strong execution across our operations, and robust free cash flow generation.  Combined with lower cash operating costs, we helped strengthen margins.  Each of these developments fundamentally improves our business and better positions EOG Resources, Inc. going forward as being among the highest return and lowest cost producers with strong environmental performance.
